    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='221:248'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-1a' );" name="017-1a" class="pb">[017-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='248:261'>禮記要義卷第十八　學記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='261:271'>　一鄭氏不見說命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='271:291'>兊命曰念終始典于學其此之謂乎注云典經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='291:311'>也言學之不舎業也兊當爲說字之誤也髙宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='311:331'>夢傳說求而得之作說命三篇在尚書今亡正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='331:351'>義曰其事具尚書篇見在鄭云今亡者鄭不見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='351:359'>古文尚書故也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='359:373'>　二古者立學之制入學之序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='373:393'>古之教者家有塾黨有庠術有序國有學比年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='393:420'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-1b' );" name="017-1b" class="pb">[017-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='420:440'>入學中年考校一年視離經辨志三年視敬業</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='440:460'>樂羣五年視博習親師七年視論學取友謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='460:480'>小成九年知類通逹強立而不反謂之大成注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='480:500'>云術當爲遂聲之誤也古者仕焉而巳者歸教</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='500:520'>於閭里朝夕坐於門門側之堂謂之塾周禮五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='520:540'>百家爲黨萬二千五百家爲遂黨屬於郷遂在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='540:560'>逺郊之外學者每歳來入也中猶間也郷遂大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='560:580'>夫間歳則考學者之德行道藝周禮三年大比</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='580:600'>乃考焉離經斷句絶也辨志謂別其心意所趣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='600:627'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-2a' );" name="017-2a" class="pb">[017-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='627:647'>郷也知類知事義之比也強立臨事不惑也不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='647:655'>反不違失師道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='655:669'>　三家塾黨庠術序國學之制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='669:689'>家有塾者此明學之所在周禮百里之内二十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='689:709'>五家爲閭同共一巷巷首有門門邊有塾謂民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='709:729'>在家之時朝夕岀入恒受教於塾故云家有塾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='729:749'>白虎通云古之教民百里皆有師里中之老有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='749:769'>道德者爲里右師其次爲左師教里中之子弟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='769:788'>以道藝孝悌仁義也黨有庠者黨謂周禮五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='788:815'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-2b' );" name="017-2b" class="pb">[017-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='815:835'>百家也庠學名也於黨中立學教閭中所升者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='835:855'>也　術有序者術遂之周禮萬二千五百家爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='855:875'>遂遂有序亦學名於遂中立學教黨學所升者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='875:895'>也　國有學者國謂天子所都及諸侯國中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='895:915'>周禮天子立四代學以教丗子羣后之子及郷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='915:935'>中俊選所升之士也而尊魯亦立四代學餘諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='935:952'>侯於國但立時王之學故云國有學也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='952:965'>　四父師少師教于左右塾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='965:985'>案書傳說云大夫七十而致仕而退老歸其郷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='985:1012'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-3a' );" name="017-3a" class="pb">[017-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1012:1032'>里大夫爲父師士爲少師新榖巳入餘子皆入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1032:1052'>學距冬至四十三日始出學上老平明坐於右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1052:1072'>塾庶老坐於左塾餘子畢出然後皆歸夕亦如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1072:1075'>之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1075:1086'>五黨學曰序此經曰庠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1086:1106'>案周禮遂人掌野之官百里之外故知遂在逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1106:1126'>郊之外鄭注州長職云序州黨之學則黨學曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1126:1146'>序此云黨有庠者郷學曰庠故郷飲酒之義云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1146:1166'>主人拜迎賔于庠門之外注云庠郷學也州黨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1166:1193'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-3b' );" name="017-3b" class="pb">[017-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1193:1213'>曰序此云黨有庠者是郷之所居黨爲郷學之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1213:1233'>庠不别立序凡六郷之内州學以下皆爲庠六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1233:1253'>遂之内縣學以下皆爲序也皇氏云遂學曰庠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1253:1273'>與此文違其義非也庾氏云黨有庠謂夏殷禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1273:1282'>非周法義或然也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1282:1290'>　六中年考校</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1290:1310'>應入大學者自國家考校之耳其未入大學者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1310:1319'>郷遂大夫考校也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1319:1329'>七大胥以皷徴學士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1329:1356'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-4a' );" name="017-4a" class="pb">[017-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1356:1376'>入學皷篋孫其業也　入學謂學士入學之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1376:1396'>大胥之官先擊皷以召之學者旣至發其筐篋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1396:1416'>以出其書故云皷篋也所以然者欲使學者孫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1416:1436'>其業謂恭順其所持經業故大胥云用樂者以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1436:1456'>皷徴學士文王丗子云大昕皷徴所以警衆也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1456:1476'>文王丗子云謂天子視學之時擊皷警衆也若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1476:1496'>是凡常入學用樂及爲祭祀用樂者以皷徴學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1496:1501'>士是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1501:1515'>　　天子卜禘及大禮皆視學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1515:1542'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-4b' );" name="017-4b" class="pb">[017-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1542:1562'>云天子諸侯旣祭乃視學者謂於夏祭之時旣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1562:1582'>爲禘祭之後乃視學考校當禘祭之年故云未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1582:1602'>卜禘不視學若不當禘祭之年待時祭之後乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1602:1622'>視學也此視學謂考試學者經業或君親徃或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1622:1642'>使有司爲之非天子大禮視學也若大禮視學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1642:1662'>在仲春仲秋及季春故文王丗子云凡大合樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1662:1682'>必遂養老注云大合樂謂春入學舎菜合舞秋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1682:1702'>頒學合聲於是時也天子則視學焉月令季春</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1702:1722'>大合樂天子率三公九卿而視學焉與此别也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1722:1749'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-5a' );" name="017-5a" class="pb">[017-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1749:1769'>視學旣在夏祭之後則天子春秋視學亦應在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1769:1789'>春秋時祭之後此舉未卜禘不視學則餘可知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1789:1792'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1792:1802'>　　藏脩息遊於學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1802:1822'>藏焉脩焉息焉遊焉注云藏謂懷抱之脩習也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1822:1842'>息謂作勞休止於之息遊謂間暇無事於之遊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1842:1852'>　　離師輔而不反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1852:1872'>是以雖離師輔而不反也者輔即友也友主切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1872:1892'>磋是輔己之道深逺也離猶違也已道深明不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1892:1919'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-5b' );" name="017-5b" class="pb">[017-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1919:1939'>復虚妄心自信之若假令違離師友獨在一處</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1939:1959'>而講說不違反於師友昔日之意旨此則強立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1959:1964'>不反也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1964:1975'>　　呻其佔畢多其訊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1975:1995'>今之教者呻其佔畢多其訊注云呻吟也佔視</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1995:2015'>也簡謂之畢訊猶問也言今之師自不曉經之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2015:2035'>義但吟誦其所視簡之文多其難間也呻或爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2035:2042'>慕訊或爲訾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2042:2054'>　　和易以思可謂善喻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2054:2081'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-6a' );" name="017-6a" class="pb">[017-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2081:2101'>故君子之教諭也道而弗牽強而弗抑開而弗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2101:2121'>逹道而弗牽則和強而弗抑則易開而弗逹則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2121:2141'>思和易以思可謂善喻矣注云道示之以道塗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2141:2161'>也抑猶推也開爲發頭角思而得之則深正義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2161:2181'>曰若人苟不曉而牽偪之則彼心必生忿恚師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2181:2201'>與弟子不復和親今若但示正道寛柔教之則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2201:2221'>彼心和而意乃覺悟也强而弗抑則易者賀氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2221:2241'>以爲師但勸強其神識而不抑之令曉則受者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2241:2261'>和易和易亦易成也　開而弗逹則思者但開</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2261:2288'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-6b' );" name="017-6b" class="pb">[017-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2288:2308'>發義理而不爲通逹使學者用意思念思則必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2308:2311'>深</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2311:2324'>　語而不知舎之以須其後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2324:2344'>力不能問然後語之語之而不知雖舎之可也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2344:2364'>注云舎之湏後正義曰若受業者才力苟不能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2364:2384'>見問待憤憤悱悱之間則師然後乃示語之矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2384:2404'>語之而不知雖舎之可也者弟子旣不能問因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2404:2424'>而語之語之不能知且舎住待後別更語之可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2424:2427'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2427:2454'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-7a' );" name="017-7a" class="pb">[017-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2454:2468'>　　始駕馬者反之車在馬前</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2468:2488'>始駕馬者反之車在馬前者此第三譬明新習</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2488:2508'>者也始駕者謂馬子始學駕車之時反之者駕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2508:2528'>馬之法大馬本駕在車前今將馬子繫隨車後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2528:2548'>而行故云反之車在馬前所以然者此駒旣未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2548:2568'>曽駕車若忽駕之必當驚奔今以大馬牽車於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2568:2588'>前而繫駒於後使此駒日日見車之行其駒慣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2588:2599'>習而後駕之不復驚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2599:2609'>　　五服非師不親</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2609:2636'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-7b' );" name="017-7b" class="pb">[017-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2636:2656'>師無當於五服五服弗得不親者師教之師也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2656:2676'>五服斬衰也齊衰也大功也小功也緦麻也師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2676:2696'>於弟子不當五服之一也而弟子之家若無師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2696:2710'>教誨則五服之情不相和親也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2710:2726'>　　大時不齊四時草木各有生死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2726:2746'>大時不齊者大時謂天時也齊謂一時同也天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2746:2766'>生殺不共在一時猶春夏華卉自生薺麥自死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2766:2784'>秋冬草木自死而薺麥自生故云不齊也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2784:2796'>　　三王祭河而後祭海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2796:2823'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '017-8a' );" name="017-8a" class="pb">[017-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2823:2843'>三主祭百川之時皆先祭河而後祭海也或先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2843:2863'>祭其源或後祭其委河爲海本源爲委本皆曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2863:2883'>川也皇氏以爲河海之外源之與委也今依用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2883:2903'>焉或解云源則河也委則海也申明先河而後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2903:2923'>海義亦通矣其始一勺也後至不測也猶言學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2923:2935'>𥘉爲積漸後成賢聖也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2935:2945'>禮記要義卷第十八</span><br/>
